Contribute

How can you help?

  • You can follow us on twitter @OKFN_AU and spread the word.
  • Embed the census in your web site.
  • Make a submission about open data you're familar with.
  • Suggest an improvement. We're always looking for ways to improve.
  • Add your location to the census.
  • Contribute to the census open source project on Github.
